Description: Provides an interactive Shiny application for plant breeding 
    analyses, including designing experiments (RCBD, Augmented RCBD, Alpha 
    Lattice), analyzing experimental data, mating design analytics, 
    stability analysis, and multivariate analysis. Designed for 
    non-programmers with a point-and-click interface.
